{"tid":277710,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"權志龍","createTime":"2017-06-09T23:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T03:30:52.000Z","uid":98551,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eacf1d4eebde122d87e2f9c77d3faa43255c09ed","tid":277710,"uid":98551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T23:42:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2094384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2094384&d=miRruejfEI4R7cScey8rnBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=384a9dc9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2094384&h=e12b2515\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2094384</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔娛樂頻道／綜合報導〕南韓天團BIGBANG隊長「G-DRAGON」權志龍，睽違4年推出新專輯《權志龍》，這次專輯一別過去HipHop歌路，主打抒情歌，讓他在短短1天內便在世界39國的音樂平台取得冠軍，創下韓星歷史。<br />\nGD8日發行新專輯《權志龍》，因同團員爆出呼麻事件，此次專輯宣傳較為低調，原本許多粉絲擔心GD受到影響，沒想到發行後短短1天內（9日南韓時間6時），GD新專輯便奪下台灣、法國、泰國、香港、美國、丹麥、西班牙等39個國家的iTunes音源平台冠軍，在南韓國內知名的8個音樂平台也都獲得第一名，創下韓星歷史新紀錄，讓許多歌迷激動落淚。"},{"pid":"c973f29fc6fdc0558c9c335bd6f44b6f1df1a133","tid":277710,"uid":20291,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T23:53:24.000Z","msg":"真心唔識欣賞泡菜音樂"},{"pid":"470d024db8cfbc4c22ad3391b3631f65b73e7a3e","tid":277710,"uid":15249,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T23:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班推左幾個post話bigbang要收皮<br />\n點知即刻破紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全世界有幾多個明星可以做到？"},{"pid":"7c1c72c8a1d794a1afec6e71fd7fefd6bbcde583","tid":277710,"uid":78072,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T23:55:04.000Z","msg":"激動流淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":